Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an1\pos(970,528)}還好嗎？大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an1\pos(968,122)}還好嗎？大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.40,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an1\pos(440,740)}今天我準備去安達家看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an1\pos(440,685)}今天我準備去安達家看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:39.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an1\pos(1253.333,685)}可以嗎??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an1\pos(544,333)}今天我準備去安達家看看… 可以嗎??
